    • deduce

      public static Meta.CursorFactory deduce(List<ColumnMetaData> columns, Class resultClazz)
      Deduces the appropriate CursorFactory for accessing the underlying result set. For result sets composed by records, resultClazz must be not null, and each field name in columns must match one of its public fields.
      Parameters:
      columns - The columns metadata for the result set
      resultClazz - The class representing the records, if any
      Returns:
      the appropriate CursorFactory for the underlying result set
      Throws:
      RuntimeException - if the field name validation fails
